{"id":2615,"date":"2025-06-16T17:17:18","date_gmt":"2025-06-16T10:17:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2615"},"modified":"2025-06-19T11:39:56","modified_gmt":"2025-06-19T04:39:56","slug":"biowhite-infusion-workshop-su-kien-dinh-hinh-chuan-muc-moi-trong-tham-my-da-lieu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/biowhite-infusion-workshop-su-kien-dinh-hinh-chuan-muc-moi-trong-tham-my-da-lieu\/","title":{"rendered":"Biowhite infusion workshop &#8211; S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c m\u1edbi trong th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 da li\u1ec5u"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a workshop l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a GSC l\u00e0 <\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u201cGI\u1ea2I M\u00c3 C\u00d4NG NGH\u1ec6 C\u1ea4Y TR\u1eaeNG T\u1ebe B\u00c0O CHU\u1ea8N Y KHOA\u201d &#8211; Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u00e0i to\u00e1n gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u00eau ch\u00ed an to\u00e0n l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u1edd v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u01a1n 40 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng VIP.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2708\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2708\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2708\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9370_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"GI\u1ea2I M\u00c3 C\u00d4NG NGH\u1ec6 C\u1ea4Y TR\u1eaeNG T\u1ebe B\u00c0O CHU\u1ea8N Y KHOA\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9370_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9370_result-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9370_result-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9370_result-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9370_result-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9370_result-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9370_result-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2708\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GI\u1ea2I M\u00c3 C\u00d4NG NGH\u1ec6 C\u1ea4Y TR\u1eaeNG T\u1ebe B\u00c0O CHU\u1ea8N Y KHOA<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng VIP tham gia, GSC r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb qu\u00fd anh ch\u1ecb v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb. S\u1ef1 h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1ee9ng t\u1eeb qu\u00fd anh em gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i workshop ti\u1ebfp theo b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Workshop l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham gia d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Thu Th\u1ea3o c\u00f9ng chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u Kim Nhung \u2013 b\u00e1c s\u0129 v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 5 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ng\u00e0nh, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho h\u01a1n 200 Spa, Clinic v\u00e0 TMV \u0111ang h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi GSC tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2723\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2723\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2723 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Thu Th\u1ea3o\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9649_result-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2723\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Thu Th\u1ea3o<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap qu\u00fd ch\u1ee7 Spa\/ Clinic\/ TMV n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n trong ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u00e3ng d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ti\u00ean phong \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng khoa h\u1ecdc ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn. Bu\u1ed5i workshop c\u1ee7a GSC \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb t\u1edbi c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ea1m da, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 m\u1edbi \u201cph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ea5y nano tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2706\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2706\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2706\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9343_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham gia event\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9343_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9343_result-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9343_result-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9343_result-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9343_result-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9343_result-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9343_result-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2706\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi tham gia event<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi chia s\u1ebb d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u, nh\u1eefng thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1c s\u0129 GSC chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ho\u00e1 h\u01a1n. Gi\u00fap t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi nh\u1edb c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c. Gi\u00fap t\u0103ng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng \u201cch\u1ed1t deal vip\u201d \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n cho SPA c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2718\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2718\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2718\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9611_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"M\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u worshop gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh c\u1ea5y tr\u1eafng 2025\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9611_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9611_result-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9611_result-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9611_result-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9611_result-1536x864.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9611_result-2048x1152.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9611_result-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2718\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u worshop gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh c\u1ea5y tr\u1eafng 2025<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n trong workshop l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 BioWhite Infusion, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u1ea5y tr\u1eafng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 nano, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a GSC.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng theo quy tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n Y khoa, mang \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 an to\u00e0n, r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2726\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2726\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2726\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9715_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 \u1ee7 tr\u1eafng c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng GSC\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9715_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9715_result-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9715_result-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9715_result-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9715_result-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9715_result-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9715_result-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2726\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 \u1ee7 tr\u1eafng c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng GSC<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1edd t\u00ednh an to\u00e0n cao, khi c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o da b\u1eb1ng h\u1ea1t nano si\u00eau nh\u1ecf, d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng hay t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, gi\u1ea3m t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, n\u00e1m, th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng d\u00e0i. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 vitamin C v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a c\u0169ng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u00e0n da t\u1eeb s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe cho da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 bu\u1ed5i workshop di\u1ec5n ra trong kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed h\u00e2n hoan vui v\u1ebb, b\u1eb1ng format ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh m\u1edbi l\u1ea1 nh\u01b0 game v\u1ec1 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c hay th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u gi\u00fap kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ghi nh\u1edb bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e0 m\u00e0 GSC trao g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd ch\u1ee7 spa\/clinic nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n m\u00e0 GSC mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi g\u1eafm t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n qu\u00e0 d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng game vui t\u1ea1i bu\u1ed5i workshop.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2722\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2722\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2722\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9645_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c GSC v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9645_result-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9645_result-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9645_result-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9645_result-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9645_result-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9645_result-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9645_result-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2722\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c GSC v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2728\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2728\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2728\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/IMG_9796_result-scaled.webp\" alt=\"S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n GSC\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" s